Genetic data. BIN : BOLD :ADR9019 (n=1 from Ethiopia ). Three supposedly conspecific DNA barcodes from Yemen (cf. Hausmann 2006 ) at a genetic distance of 2.7–3.0% (short sequence fragments), requiring further, integrative taxonomic research.
Distribution. Algeria , Ethiopia , Kenya , Saudi Arabia , Tanzania , Yemen ( Rothschild 1915 ; Fletcher 1974 , 1958 ; Wiltshire 1980 ; Hausmann 1999 ).
